                    "text": "<p>Do you have a website or blog interested in the Bonds Creek Knives Affiliate program? If so, apply here to join our program and earn a commission on every qualified buyer you send our way. We’ve worked hard to optimize our site for high conversions, which translates to more dollars in your pocket.</p><p><strong>Program Description:</strong><br/>Bonds Creek Knives is a premium American knife brand built for hunters, outdoorsmen, and hardworking everyday carry users. Every knife is made in West Virginia, backed by a lifetime warranty, and designed to be used in the field, not left sitting on a shelf. The brand positions itself as “hunter built” and “field proven,” with a product lineup centered on purpose-built knives for hunting, field dressing, everyday work, and life outdoors. </p><p></p><p>At Bonds Creek Knives, craftsmanship and function come first. The brand highlights that its knives are made in West Virginia, built by hunters for hunters, and supported by a lifetime warranty against defects in materials and craftsmanship. The site also promotes free shipping on orders over $200 and offers discounts through GovX ID for military, first responders, medical workers, and teachers. </p><p></p><p>The Bonds Creek Knives affiliate program is designed for quality content creators, publishers, and partners whose audiences value American-made gear, hunting, rugged craftsmanship, and premium outdoor products. Affiliates have the opportunity to promote a fast-growing knife brand with strong visual appeal, authentic field use cases, and a product story rooted in American manufacturing and real-world performance. We are looking to partner with affiliates who can represent the brand in a way that aligns with its premium positioning and outdoor lifestyle audience.</p><p> </p><ul><li><strong>12% </strong>Commission for Content Publishers/Coupon/Deal/Sub Affiliate networks on every sale</li><li><strong>30-day</strong> cookie duration</li><li>High Average Order Value</li><li>Strong Website Conversion Rate</li><li>Excellent Marketing Materials</li></ul>",
